asciifire
---------
Copyright 2009 (c) Papadopoulos Nikos <nikpapas@gmail.com>

About
-----
asciifire is the classic fire effect, implemented in javascript.
It renders the flames in ascii text.

Usage
-----
Include the script in your page, place a <pre id="fire"></pre> tag 
in your page source and call the fire() function. To setup the effect 
use the following functions:

* setupFire(width, height) : Sets the width and height
* reversePalette()         : Reverses the pallet
* setTransparency(setting) : Controls the transparency. Expects 0 or 1.

